text: Lathan Toland is an American actor best known for his role on ABC Family's Becoming Us, which was produced by Ryan Seacrest. Prior to this Toland co- starred in an independent film called Innocent in 2009 with Alexa Vega. ==Filmography== ===Film & Television=== {| class="wikitable sortable" ! Year ! Title !
